Class PublicField

  • Object
    • PublicField
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    InstanceField, StaticField, StaticFinalField

    public abstract class PublicField
extends Object
implements Serializable
    PublicField is an abstract class representing a public field of a class object, which can be an instance field, a static field, or a static final field. Each is implemented as a separate class. Meant to be adapted by either FieldSetter or FieldGetter for use as a StatementKind.
    See Also:
    InstanceField, StaticField, StaticFinalField, Serialized Form
